articles.title: The Canadian behind The Flash explains what it takes to design a blockbuster
articles.description: There’s an Oscar-winning Canadian behind a major new super hero movie. Much of the news coverage for DC's The Flash has centred on controversial actor Ezra Miller, but the film’s world was created by Toronto-based production designer Paul Austerberry.
